  Opportunities for Scientists and Physicians

   Interested in the big picture? NINDS seeks bold, visionary scientists
   and physicians with a broad knowledge of neuroscience. As a Program
   Director, you will conceive and develop large-scale funding
   initiatives, organize workshops, and interact with leading
   neuroscientists throughout the world. Successful candidates will join a
   highly interactive group of scientists and clinicians applying their
   basic, translational, and clinical experience and expertise in all
   areas of neuroscience.

  All Openings at NINDS

   CareerHere is an online system that allows potential applicants to
   review job openings and provides a means to create and submit a resume.
   Apply on-line now!

   For photos and profiles of some of our Program Directors and Scientific
   Review Administrators please visit this webpage.

